des:
Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created completely to motivate you, in your everyday routine, If you like it kindly give us rating and comments

The person who reads this message is beautiful and have a great day
